^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Now, if you are the partner of the 3N opener and you end up getting doubled, if you don't have any tricks, you probably want to pull the double. If doubled, redouble tells partner to bid her suit. If not doubled, then 4C says pass or correct. Here I wanted to double them in whatever they played. I only had 1 club, and had enough stuff outside that I felt we would beat them. Had I decided I did not want to defend 4S, I can bid 4N to ask Kerrie to bid her suit.|
