^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Many people play that they can make a cue bid of the overcalled suit with only 3 card support. But, I like to play it shows 4 card support. The reason I like it to show 4 card support is that a 9 card fit is much better than an 8 card fit. So, I want to know when we have a 9 card fit. However, then on hands where you have 3 card support and limit raise points, you might have to make an awkward call.|
